<item>
            <title>[PIG-713] Autocompletion doesn&apos;t complete aliases</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-713</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Autocompletion only knows about keywords, but in different contexts, it would be nice if it completed aliases where an alias is expected.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
